# accounts.mojo - Cursor Rules

> **Globale Standards:** `/root/projects/CODING_STANDARDS.md`

## Projekt-Info

- **Typ:** Account/User Management (SSOT für Tenants)
- **Domain:** account.mojo-institut.de
- **Stack:** Next.js + Fastify + Prisma

## Architektur

```
apps/
├── web/        # Frontend (Next.js)
└── api/        # Backend API (Fastify)
packages/
└── shared/     # Shared Types
```

## Wichtige Patterns

1. **Single Source of Truth:** Tenant-Daten werden hier verwaltet
2. **Auth:** Clerk JWT + Clerk Webhooks für User/Org Sync
3. **Multitenancy:** `@mojo/tenant` Middleware

## Service-to-Service

Andere Apps rufen accounts.mojo für Tenant-Daten:
- Headers: `x-tenant-id`, `x-tenant-slug`, `x-service-name`
